342","type":"question","created":1678034791,"answer_count":73,"follower_count":132,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[806,41509,126081,141127],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如题，事情已经过去十年了，但我一直耿耿于怀。 父亲在我初中的时候去世，去世前跟亲戚一起合伙做生意（开工厂，占50%股份，亲戚是父亲的亲妹妹和妹夫），在去世后刚过几天，亲戚就上门说要分生意，要求我们退出工厂，用现金买我们的股份。但实际上亲戚现金不够，最后结果是，工厂全归他们，现金分批还给我们（有计利益），但工厂的所有收益跟我们无关。据我所知，当时市场环境很好，亲戚很快就换车换房。 补充一点，当时家族长辈说不能这么绝情，起码要等我父亲去世过百日，最后过百日后，亲戚在第101天（如果没记错）就上门，最后拆伙。 我记得当时我亲眼看着亲戚上门要求拆伙，但当时不太懂这意味着什么，现在参加工作有一段时间，始终对这件事耿耿于怀。 并且我对亲戚是不太感冒的，一直认为有需要帮忙时，始终亲戚不如自己认识的朋友，平时只有过年才会见一面。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IqN28j5Pz0tMkEAMaCDkyODk4ODAyIOeOk6AGMAM4hAFAIXIJNTg3Nzc3MzQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"53 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1678227253.0180664","card_id":"Q_587796689","target":{"id":587796689,"title":"为什么看似很笨的郭靖能成为绝顶高手？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/587796689","type":"question","created":1678055494,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[23433,40769,48670],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IqN28j5Pz0tMkEAMaCDkyOTAzMTYzIMawlKAGMAA4PUAicgk1ODc3OTY2ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"53 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"35_1678227253.0186296","card_id":"Q_587587737","target":{"id":587587737,"title":"如何看待在小虎离队后，RNG 的 2023 春季赛队伍状态断崖式下滑？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/587587737","type":"question","created":1677931868,"answer_count":34,"follower_count":36,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":